{"lemma":"فَلَجَ","slug":"فَلَجَ","root":"ف.ل.ج","root_slug":"ف-ل-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ل-ج","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34447"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فُلِجَ (fulija) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"diastema"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a small river"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of فُلِجَ (fulija, “to become paralyzed”)."},"ipa":["/fa.lad͡ʒ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34447","headword_ar":"فَلَجَ","root":"flj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, L, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or the latter only [when the verb is trans. as] in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja Alqawoma","text_ar":"فَلَجَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falojN","text_ar":"فَلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuluwjN","text_ar":"فُلُوجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or both, and, accord. to Kr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulojN","text_ar":"فُلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajN","text_ar":"فَلَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but it is said in the L that these two are simple substs: (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aflj","text_ar":"افلج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifolaAjN","text_ar":"اـِفْلَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) the latter verb authorized by AO and Ktr and others, but omitted by Th in the Fs; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He succeeded; succeeded in an enterprise"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a contest; overcame, conquered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gained a victory:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, &c.:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he attained his object; gained what he sought."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano yaA^oti AlHakama waHodhu yafolujo","text_ar":"مَنْ يَاْتِ الحَكَمَ وَحْدهُ يَفْلُجْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who comes to the judge by himself will succeed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcome,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gain his cause"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a proverb. (S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja","text_ar":"فَلَجَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY xaSomihi","text_ar":"عَلَى خَصْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aflj","text_ar":"افلج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"succeeded against,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcame, his adversary;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"got before him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"got precedence of him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja biHuj~atihi","text_ar":"فَلَجَ بِحُجَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Huj~atihi","text_ar":"فِى حُجَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He established,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he overcame by"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his argument, plea, allegation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajato Huj~atuhu","text_ar":"فَلَجَتْ حُجَّتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His argument,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was successful"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja sahomuhu","text_ar":"فَلَجَ سَهْمُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aflj","text_ar":"افلج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His arrow was successful."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajato biqalobiY","text_ar":"فَلَجَتْ بِقَلْبِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took away"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"captivated"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"my heart."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja Alqawoma","text_ar":"فَلَجَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which case only one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafoluju","text_ar":"يَفْلُجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafoliju","text_ar":"يَفْلِجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja","text_ar":"فَلَجَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHaAbaha","text_ar":"اَصْحَابَهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"succeeded against,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcame, the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his companions."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja","text_ar":"فَلَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, L, K,) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or the former only, (MF. TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falojN","text_ar":"فَلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He divided"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parted"},{"kind":"text","text":"it;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divided"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in parts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shares;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distributed"},{"kind":"text","text":"it: (S, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fl~j","text_ar":"فلّج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafoliyjN","text_ar":"تَفْلِيجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he divided"},{"kind":"text","text":"property, (Mgh, TA,) or running water: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he divided"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in halves."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, Msb, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajatu Al$~aYo'a bayonahumo","text_ar":"فَلَجَتُ الشَّىْءَ بَيْنَهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I divided, parted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distributed, the thing between them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja Al$~aYo'a bayonahumaA","text_ar":"فَلَجَ الشَّىْءَ بَيْنَهُمَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He divided the thing between them two in halves."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajotu A^alofFA","text_ar":"فَلَجْتُ اَلْفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falojN","text_ar":"فَلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuluwjN","text_ar":"فُلُوجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I divided, parted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distributed, a thousand"},{"kind":"text","text":"[dirhems]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"filoj","text_ar":"فِلْج"},{"kind":"text","text":", a well-known measure of capacity. (Msb.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajotu","text_ar":"فَلَجْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, *) aor. in this case and in other cases following"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":"only, (TA,) [but it is implied in the S and O and Msb that it is"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falojN","text_ar":"فَلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I split the thing, clave it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divided it lengthwise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I split the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into two halves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajotu Al$~aYo'a falojayoni","text_ar":"فَلَجْتُ الشَّىْءَ فَلْجَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has this latter meaning. (S, O.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajotu AlA^aroDa lilz~iraAEapi","text_ar":"فَلَجْتُ الاَرْضَ لِلزِّرَاعَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K, *) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falojN","text_ar":"فَلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaHotuhaA","text_ar":"فَلَحْتُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I furrowed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ploughed, the land for sowing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yafoluju AlA^amora","text_ar":"هُوَ يَفْلُجُ الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looks into, and divides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distributes, and manages, the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja","text_ar":"فَلَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falojN","text_ar":"فَلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He imposed"},{"kind":"text","text":"the [tax called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jizuyap","text_ar":"جِزُيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja","text_ar":"فَلَجَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljizoyapa EalaY Alqawomi","text_ar":"الجِزْيَةَ عَلَى القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, Mgh, * O, &c.,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja Alqawoma","text_ar":"فَلَجَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He imposed the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jzyp","text_ar":"جزية"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Mgh, O, &c.:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he divided the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jzyp","text_ar":"جزية"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, imposing upon each person his portion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, Mgh; *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaja Aljizoyapa bayonahumo","text_ar":"فَلَجَ الجِزْيَةَ بَيْنَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) [said to be] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"filojN","text_ar":"فِلْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAlijN","text_ar":"فَالِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqafiyzuAlfaAliju","text_ar":"القَفِيزُالفَالِجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A'Obeyd, S, O;) signifying a certain measure of capacity; because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jzyh","text_ar":"جزيه"},{"kind":"text","text":"used to he paid in wheat, or corn: (As, Mgh:) or the verb in this sense is an arabicized word. (Shifá el-Ghaleel.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falija","text_ar":"فَلِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajN","text_ar":"فَلَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajapN","text_ar":"فَلَجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falajN","text_ar":"فَلَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning [as expl. below, i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"width. between the teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feet"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"legs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms"},{"kind":"text","text":"], &c. (Lh, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falija","text_ar":"فَلِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Th, S, O, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAlijN","text_ar":"فَالِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", one of the [few] inf. as. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (ISd, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falija","text_ar":"فَلِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", mentioned by IKtt and Es-Sarakustee and others; (MF, TA;) but the former alone is mentioned by Th in the Fs, and by other celebrated lexicologists; (TA;) [and vulg. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Anfj","text_ar":"انفج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had the disease termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaAliju","text_ar":"الفَالِجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. below]. (Th, S, O. Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","O","L","Msb","K","TA","Mgh","A","As","Th"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}